<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَمِنْ مَكَارِمِهَا عَشْرٌ عَلَيْكَ بِهَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَإِنَّهَا حِكَمٌ تُرْوَى عَنِ الأَثَرِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>صِدْقُ الْحَدِيثِ فَلا تَعْدِلْ بِهِ خُلُقًا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>تَبْلُغُ مِنَ الْمَجْدِ أَبْهَى بَاذِخُ السُّرَرِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَكُنْ خَلِيقًا بِصِدْقِ الْبَأْسِ يَوْم وَغَى<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَشَرُّ عَيْبِ الْفَتَى بِالْجبْنِ وَالْخُورِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أَجِبْ مُنَادِي الْعُلَى فِي خَوْضِ غَمْرَتِهَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَالْعِزّ تَحْتَ ظِلالِ الْبِيضِ وَالسّمرِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>بِالصَّبْرِ يَكْتَسِبُ الْمِقْدَامُ نُصْرَتُهُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَيَلْبِسُ الضِّدَّ مِنْهُ ثَوب مُنْذَعِرِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَلا يُدْنِّي لَهُ الإِقْدَامُ مِنْ أَجَلٍ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>يَكْفِي حِرَاسَتُهُ مُسْتَأْخِرُ الْقَدَرِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَاحْرِصْ عَلَى عَمَلِ الْمَعْرُوفِ مُجْتَهِدًا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَإِنَّ ذَلِكَ أَرْجَى كُلّ مُنْتَظِر<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَلَيْسَ مِنْ حَالَةْ تَبْقَى كَهَيْئَتِهَا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَاغْنَمْ زَمَان الصَّفَاء خَوْفًا مِنَ الْكَدَرِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَلا يَضِيعُ وَإِنْ طَالَ الزَّمَانُ بِهِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>مَعْرُوف مُسْتَبْصِرٍ أُنْثَى أَوْ الذَّكَرِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>إِنْ لَمْ تُصَادِفْ لَهُ أَهْلاً فَأَنْتَ إِذًا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>كُنْ أَهْلُهُ وَاصْطَنِعْهُ غَيْر مُقْتَصَر<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>أَغِثْ بِإِمْكَانِكَ الْمَلْهُوفِ حَيْثُ أَتَى<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>بِالْكَسْرِ فَاللهُ يَرْعَى حَالَ مُنْكَسِر<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>